<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>形式逻辑 on 布斯行</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/</link><description>Recent content in 形式逻辑 on 布斯行</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2020 23:19:40 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>吼呆时刻176-谬误</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-24-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB176-%E8%B0%AC%E8%AF%AF/</link><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2020 23:19:40 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-24-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB176-%E8%B0%AC%E8%AF%AF/</guid><description>谬误作为一种逻辑错误而言，诡辩乃是其最恶劣的表现。所谓诡辩乃是一种故意违反逻辑规律的要求或逻辑规则而出现的逻辑错误，也可以说是有意识地为某种谬误而作的论证。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻175-反驳</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-23-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB175-%E5%8F%8D%E9%A9%B3/</link><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jun 2020 23:12:26 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-23-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB175-%E5%8F%8D%E9%A9%B3/</guid><description>我们在论证一个论题的真实性时，常常是和批判假的论题相联系的。这是因为对和错、真与假，都是对立的统一。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻174-论证的规则</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-22-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB174-%E8%AE%BA%E8%AF%81%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%88%99/</link><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jun 2020 23:08:35 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-22-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB174-%E8%AE%BA%E8%AF%81%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%88%99/</guid><description>要使论证严密、完整、令人信服，论证就必须遵守一定的规则。论证是由论题、论据通过论证方式构成的。因此，论证的规则也分别涉及论题、论据、论证方式三个方面。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻173-论证的种类</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-21-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB173-%E8%AE%BA%E8%AF%81%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%8D%E7%B1%BB/</link><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jun 2020 22:51:42 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-21-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB173-%E8%AE%BA%E8%AF%81%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%8D%E7%B1%BB/</guid><description>按论证方式（即论证过程中所运用的推理形式）的不同，论证可分为演绎论证和归纳论证；按论证方法的不同（即是否对论题直接进行论证）可分为直接论证与间接论证。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻172-充足理由原则</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-20-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB172-%E5%85%85%E8%B6%B3%E7%90%86%E7%94%B1%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99/</link><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jun 2020 23:35:39 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-20-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB172-%E5%85%85%E8%B6%B3%E7%90%86%E7%94%B1%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99/</guid><description>事莫明于有效，论莫定于有证。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻171-论证的概念</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-19-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB171-%E8%AE%BA%E8%AF%81%E7%9A%84%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5/</link><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jun 2020 23:20:24 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-19-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB171-%E8%AE%BA%E8%AF%81%E7%9A%84%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5/</guid><description>思想是行动的指南，确定思想的真伪，是使人们有正确行动的前提。那么，如何确定一个思想的真伪呢？</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻170-排中律</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-18-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB170-%E6%8E%92%E4%B8%AD%E5%BE%8B/</link><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jun 2020 23:19:04 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-18-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB170-%E6%8E%92%E4%B8%AD%E5%BE%8B/</guid><description>在同一思维过程中，两个互相矛盾的思想不能同时是假的。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻169-矛盾律</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-17-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB169-%E7%9F%9B%E7%9B%BE%E5%BE%8B/</link><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jun 2020 22:59:51 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-17-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB169-%E7%9F%9B%E7%9B%BE%E5%BE%8B/</guid><description>在同一思维过程中，两个互相矛盾或反对的思想不能同时是真的。或者说，一个思想及其否定不能同时是真的。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻168-同一律</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-16-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB168-%E5%90%8C%E4%B8%80%E5%BE%8B/</link><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jun 2020 22:46:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-16-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB168-%E5%90%8C%E4%B8%80%E5%BE%8B/</guid><description>同一律的基本内容是：任何一个思想与其自身是等同的。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻167-假说</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-15-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB167-%E5%81%87%E8%AF%B4/</link><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jun 2020 22:44:45 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-15-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB167-%E5%81%87%E8%AF%B4/</guid><description>假说，也叫假设，它是根据已掌握的事实材料和科学原理对某一未知事物及其发展规律所作出的一种推测性的说明。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻166-类比推理</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-14-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB166-%E7%B1%BB%E6%AF%94%E6%8E%A8%E7%90%86/</link><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jun 2020 23:39:33 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-14-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB166-%E7%B1%BB%E6%AF%94%E6%8E%A8%E7%90%86/</guid><description>类比推理 一、什么是类比推理 类比推理是根据两个或两类对象在某些属性上相同，推断出它们在另外的属性上（这一属性已为类比的一个对象所具有，在另一个类比的对象那里尚未发现）也相同的一种推理。 性质类比推理是根据两个或两类对象在某些性质上的相同或相似，又知其中一个或一类对象还具有另外一种性质，从而推知另一个或一类对象也具有这另外一种性质的类比推理。 二、提高类比推理结论的可靠性 类比推理的结论虽然只具有或然性，但这种推理形式在人们的认识活动中还是具有重要作用的。 类比推理是人们在日常思维活动过程中经常运用的一种思维形式。因为，人们在实践活动中，常常要借助某些已经认识的个别事物与其他相似的事物比较，从它们之间已知的共同点出发，进一步判明它们在另一些方面的共同点，从而扩大人们的认识领域，从对某些特殊事物的认识过渡到对另一些特殊事物的认识。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻165-探求因果联系</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-13-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB165-%E6%8E%A2%E6%B1%82%E5%9B%A0%E6%9E%9C%E8%81%94%E7%B3%BB/</link><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jun 2020 23:33:04 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-13-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB165-%E6%8E%A2%E6%B1%82%E5%9B%A0%E6%9E%9C%E8%81%94%E7%B3%BB/</guid><description>客观世界是一个有内在联系的统一整体，其中各个对象或现象是互相密切联系着，互相依赖着，互相制约着的。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻164-完全归纳推理</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-12-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB164-%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A8%E5%BD%92%E7%BA%B3%E6%8E%A8%E7%90%86/</link><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jun 2020 23:45:39 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-12-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB164-%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A8%E5%BD%92%E7%BA%B3%E6%8E%A8%E7%90%86/</guid><description>根据对某类对象的全部个别对象的考察，发现它们每一个都具有某种性质，因而得出结论说：该类对象都具有某种性质。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻163-观察、实验</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-11-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB163-%E8%A7%82%E5%AF%9F%E5%AE%9E%E9%AA%8C/</link><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jun 2020 22:44:34 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-11-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB163-%E8%A7%82%E5%AF%9F%E5%AE%9E%E9%AA%8C/</guid><description>观察与一般的感觉、知觉不同。观察是依据某种确定的目的有计划地进行的。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻162-归纳推理</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-10-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB162-%E5%BD%92%E7%BA%B3%E6%8E%A8%E7%90%86/</link><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jun 2020 23:23:11 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-10-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB162-%E5%BD%92%E7%BA%B3%E6%8E%A8%E7%90%86/</guid><description>归纳推理的前提是一些关于个别事物或现象的命题，而结论则是关于该类事物或现象的普遍性命题。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻161-模态推理</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-09-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB161-%E6%A8%A1%E6%80%81%E6%8E%A8%E7%90%86/</link><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jun 2020 23:09:14 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-09-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB161-%E6%A8%A1%E6%80%81%E6%8E%A8%E7%90%86/</guid><description>骄兵必败，所以，骄兵不可能不败。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻160-模态命题</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-08-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB160-%E6%A8%A1%E6%80%81%E5%91%BD%E9%A2%98/</link><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jun 2020 22:48:41 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-08-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB160-%E6%A8%A1%E6%80%81%E5%91%BD%E9%A2%98/</guid><description>从广义上说，模态命题是指一切包含有模态词（如“必然”、“可能”、“应当”、“禁止”、“允许”等等）的命题。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻159-二难推理</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-07-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB159-%E4%BA%8C%E9%9A%BE%E6%8E%A8%E7%90%86/</link><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jun 2020 23:47:48 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-07-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB159-%E4%BA%8C%E9%9A%BE%E6%8E%A8%E7%90%86/</guid><description>二难推理是由两个假言前提和一个具有二肢的选言前提联合作为前提而构成的推理。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻158-负命题</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-06-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB158-%E8%B4%9F%E5%91%BD%E9%A2%98/</link><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jun 2020 23:18:53 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-06-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB158-%E8%B4%9F%E5%91%BD%E9%A2%98/</guid><description>通过对原命题断定情况的否定而作出的命题，就叫做负命题。例如：并非一切金属都是固体。并非有的金属不是导体。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻157-假言命题</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-05-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB157-%E5%81%87%E8%A8%80%E5%91%BD%E9%A2%98/</link><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jun 2020 22:40:21 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-05-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB157-%E5%81%87%E8%A8%80%E5%91%BD%E9%A2%98/</guid><description>假言命题是断定事物情况之间条件关系的命题。如：要想做个合格的教师，就要懂点心理学。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻156-选言命题</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-04-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB156-%E9%80%89%E8%A8%80%E5%91%BD%E9%A2%98/</link><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jun 2020 22:53:46 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-04-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB156-%E9%80%89%E8%A8%80%E5%91%BD%E9%A2%98/</guid><description>选言命题是断定事物若干种可能情况的命题。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻155-联言命题</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-03-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB155-%E8%81%94%E8%A8%80%E5%91%BD%E9%A2%98/</link><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jun 2020 23:04:02 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-03-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB155-%E8%81%94%E8%A8%80%E5%91%BD%E9%A2%98/</guid><description>联言命题是断定事物的若干种情况同时存在的命题。如：他参加过亚运会，也参加过奥运会。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻154-关系命题</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-02-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB154-%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E5%91%BD%E9%A2%98/</link><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jun 2020 23:27:12 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-02-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB154-%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E5%91%BD%E9%A2%98/</guid><description>关系命题也是一种简单命题，它是断定事物与事物之间关系的命题。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻153-三段论</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-01-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB153-%E4%B8%89%E6%AE%B5%E8%AE%BA/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jun 2020 22:52:27 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-06-01-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB153-%E4%B8%89%E6%AE%B5%E8%AE%BA/</guid><description>三段论是由三个简单性质命题即直言命题所组成的。前两个命题是推理的前提，后一个命题是推理的结论。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻151-性质命题的直接推论</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-05-30-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB151-%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8%E5%91%BD%E9%A2%98%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E6%8E%A8%E8%AE%BA/</link><pubDate>Sat, 30 May 2020 22:59:14 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-05-30-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB151-%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8%E5%91%BD%E9%A2%98%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E6%8E%A8%E8%AE%BA/</guid><description>直接推理是一种最简单的演绎推理，是以一个命题为前提而推出结论的推理。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻150-性质命题</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-05-29-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB150-%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8%E5%91%BD%E9%A2%98/</link><pubDate>Fri, 29 May 2020 23:15:14 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-05-29-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB150-%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8%E5%91%BD%E9%A2%98/</guid><description>性质命题是简单命题（即本身不包含其他命题的命题）的一种，它是断定事物具有（或不具有）某种性质的命题。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻149-命题和推理</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-05-28-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB149-%E5%91%BD%E9%A2%98%E5%92%8C%E6%8E%A8%E7%90%86/</link><pubDate>Thu, 28 May 2020 23:24:47 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-05-28-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB149-%E5%91%BD%E9%A2%98%E5%92%8C%E6%8E%A8%E7%90%86/</guid><description>判断就是对事物情况有所断定的一种思维形式。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻148-划分</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-05-27-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB148-%E5%88%92%E5%88%86/</link><pubDate>Wed, 27 May 2020 23:03:51 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-05-27-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB148-%E5%88%92%E5%88%86/</guid><description>划分就是帮助我们明确概念外延，从而明确概念的另一种逻辑方法。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻147-定义</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-05-26-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB147-%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89/</link><pubDate>Tue, 26 May 2020 22:48:28 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-05-26-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB147-%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89/</guid><description>定义是揭示概念所反映的对象的特点或本质的一种逻辑方法。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻146-概念的限制</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-05-25-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB146-%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%E7%9A%84%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6/</link><pubDate>Mon, 25 May 2020 22:16:42 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-05-25-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB146-%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%E7%9A%84%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6/</guid><description>列宁说：“如果要进行讨论，就必须把概念弄清楚。”</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻145-概念间关系</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-05-24-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB145-%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%E9%97%B4%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB/</link><pubDate>Sun, 24 May 2020 23:05:44 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-05-24-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB145-%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%E9%97%B4%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB/</guid><description>客观事物是互相联系的，因而反映事物的概念之间也是互相联系的，这就形成了概念之间的各种不同关系。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻144-概念的种类</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-05-23-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB144-%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%8D%E7%B1%BB/</link><pubDate>Sat, 23 May 2020 22:05:20 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-05-23-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB144-%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%8D%E7%B1%BB/</guid><description>辨明概念的种类则有助于我们明确概念，从而准确地理解和运用概念。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻143-概念的内涵和外延</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-05-22-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB143-%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%E7%9A%84%E5%86%85%E6%B6%B5%E5%92%8C%E5%A4%96%E5%BB%B6/</link><pubDate>Fri, 22 May 2020 22:26:23 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-05-22-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB143-%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%E7%9A%84%E5%86%85%E6%B6%B5%E5%92%8C%E5%A4%96%E5%BB%B6/</guid><description>概念的内涵是指反映在概念中的事物的特性或本质，概念的外延是指反映在概念中的一个个、一类类的事物。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻142-概念的概述</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-05-21-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB142-%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%E7%9A%84%E6%A6%82%E8%BF%B0/</link><pubDate>Thu, 21 May 2020 22:58:34 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-05-21-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB142-%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%E7%9A%84%E6%A6%82%E8%BF%B0/</guid><description>概念是思维形式最基本的组成单位，是构成命题、推理的要素。因此，在研究命题、推理之前必须首先研究概念。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻141-形式逻辑的意义和方法</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-05-20-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB141-%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91%E7%9A%84%E6%84%8F%E4%B9%89%E5%92%8C%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/</link><pubDate>Wed, 20 May 2020 23:36:10 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-05-20-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB141-%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91%E7%9A%84%E6%84%8F%E4%B9%89%E5%92%8C%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/</guid><description>学习形式逻辑对于自觉地进行思维的逻辑训练，提高人们的逻辑思维能力，增强逻辑论证的力量，从而对于提高我们整个民族的理论思维水平，都具有重要的意义。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻140-形式逻辑的对象和性质</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-05-19-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB140-%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91%E7%9A%84%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%E5%92%8C%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8/</link><pubDate>Tue, 19 May 2020 23:11:42 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-05-19-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB140-%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91%E7%9A%84%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%E5%92%8C%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8/</guid><description>思维的过程乃是对客观世界的一种概括性的间接反映过程，它具有概括性和间接性的特点。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻139-直接推论-命题</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-05-18-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB139-%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E6%8E%A8%E8%AE%BA-%E5%91%BD%E9%A2%98/</link><pubDate>Mon, 18 May 2020 22:58:01 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-05-18-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB139-%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E6%8E%A8%E8%AE%BA-%E5%91%BD%E9%A2%98/</guid><description>文字方面的通式既是主词与宾词的关联，事物方面的普遍情形也就变成了本质与属性的综合。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻138-直接推论-名词</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-05-17-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB138-%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E6%8E%A8%E8%AE%BA-%E5%90%8D%E8%AF%8D/</link><pubDate>Sun, 17 May 2020 23:39:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91/2020-05-17-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB138-%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E6%8E%A8%E8%AE%BA-%E5%90%8D%E8%AF%8D/</guid><description>逻辑与知识在事实上虽然联在一块，而逻辑学与知识论不能不分开。</description></item></channel></rss>